sourcesContent:
let focusedItemTitleContainer = {
  width: "98%", 
  height: "27px",
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC",
  color: "white",
  fontSize: "17px",
  textAlign: "center",
  paddingTop: "3px",
  display: "flex",
  flexDirection: "row",
}

let focusedItemTitle = {
  width: "50%",
}

let focusedItemDD = {
  width: "97.8%", 
  height: "794px",
  borderWidth: "0px 1px 1px 1px",
  borderStyle: "solid",
  borderColor: "#e8fefd",
  position: "relative",
  backgroundColor: "#e8fefd",
}

let focusClose = {
  userSelect: "none",
  fontSize: "25px", 
  paddingRight: "16px",
  cursor: "pointer",
  transform: "rotate(45deg)"
}

let focusContentContainer = {
  height: "220px", 
  width: "29vw", 
  textAlign: "center", 
  border: "1px solid #4382BC", 
  marginBottom: "3px"
}

let focusTitle = {
  textAlign: "center", 
  fontSize: "17px", 
  fontWeight: "bold", 
  paddingTop: "9px"
}

let focusHistoryContainer = {
  backgroundColor: "white", 
  marginLeft: "8px", 
  width: "32vw", 
  height: "182px", 
  border: "1px solid black"
}

let focusedAssociatedContainer = {
  width: "32.1vw", 
  height: "447px", 
  overflowY: "scroll", 
  overflowX: "hidden", 
  marginLeft: "36px", 
  marginTop: "5px", 
  display: "block"
}

let divider = {
  height: "1px", 
  backgroundColor: "#4382BC"
}

export {
  focusedItemTitleContainer,
  focusedItemTitle,
  focusedItemDD,
  focusClose,
  focusContentContainer,
  focusTitle,
  focusHistoryContainer,
  focusedAssociatedContainer,
  divider
}
